Whilst I was living in Ilkley - our house were right straight opposite the Cow and Calf. That was on the low side of the railway, we stayed there two years and then we went to live on the top side of the railway. Still living in Ilkley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 How long did you live in this next house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Five years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 So the first house in Ilkley you were in for a long while then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Why did your family keep moving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 I don't know, we - I think we must come of gipsy stock. We never stayed long in one place you know. Where my caravan has rested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Was it anything to do with your father's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes. My father was a solicitor in Bradford. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10095870\charrsid4527623 
At Gaunt and Hendon, Bottomley and - we travelled to and - well, he did - he travelled to and from - Ilkley to Bradford. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 
And then ultimately - oh whilst we were in Ilkley I - I was invited to become a member of the - St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10095870\charrsid4527623 Margaret\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 
 Church which rather annoyed the - the then Vicar of Ilkley, very nice fellow called Jimmy Tempson, he was the Vicar, fine fellow he was. And he came to see us at home one day and she said to mother, why did you let him go to St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10095870\charrsid4527623 Margaret\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 ? He's my boy. Mother said, I don't know, couldn't tell you. Anyway I went - I joined St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10095870\charrsid4527623 Margaret\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623  choir and afterwards became solo boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 You still have a good voice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Four brothers and a sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 And the names of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Myself, Douglas.
