\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes. And there we are look. That's me at the - at that end. I was in the Artillery and the other three }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10768108\charrsid4527623 brothers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623  were in the Duke of Wellington's Regiment. Yes. And - the one next to me and the one at this end were killed in action. That's - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10095870\charrsid4527623 Clifford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 . Teddy and Cecil. Cecil was killed in Italy. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 You were the eldest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 I was the eldest, yes. Then Clifford and Clifford was born about five years after me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 And Teddy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Teddy - no, yes, Teddy was born - about nine years later.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 And Cecil?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Cecil was born - inside the twelve months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 He was the next to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Or they came after Teddy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 No, that - that is in the order of seniority or birth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 So Cecil is the youngest and he was about ten years younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes.
