\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 No, no tinned veges then. All fresh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 What about dried ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 No there wasn't such a thing then. If there was I was not aware of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 You didn't keep any livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 No. We had a dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 How many times did you get meat in the week?
