\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Well I don't know I'm sure, I mean that was up to me parents really. The time came of course when I - certain age brings a desire to be 
