\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 I had had enough luv.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 You weren't sorry to leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Oh I'd had bellyful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Do you think you benefitted by attending school?
