\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Windhill, Shipley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 She lived right opposite, or her people did, right opposite Windhill parish church where we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid878338 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 . Yes, right opposite their front door was the church. We walked across -
