 parents for quite a while. Yes. And then - in the meantime I was traveling to and from Leeds and Shipley, I was working for a firm of solicitors in Leeds and - likely on the G.P.O. And then they decided I'd - I'd better come and live in Leeds. So I bough
t a house - in - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15623808\charrsid4527623 Barclay}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623  Avenue. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15623808\charrsid4527623 Number}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623  eleven. I give three - three hundred and fifty for it. Roads unmade at the front, unmade at the back. No - no causeway, just one - one flag in front of the door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Was this the first house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes. Gas. So - I h
ad it - I arranged with the corporation, along with others, to have the road made at the front and the back. Added - altered for electricity instead of gas. And used paraffin but I don't know what I didn't do.
