\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Was it electric?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 No, gas. After - after wards had it converted though into electricity. And she was an extraordinarily good co
ok. One thing I used to love, every Sunday she made a beautiful big apple pie about that thick. Oh dear. We had next door but one neighbour in every Sunday, regularly they came just for a cup of tea and slice of apple pie. Aye.
