\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes. Yes, of course there's Yorkshire notion - beginning, where have all the taverns gone? There used to be about - eighty-nine in }{
