depended how old they were of course. 'Cos they'd be on the bottle and - no, I'm telling a lie, they were breast fed, all four of them. 'Course she didn't feed them of course at the dinner table but - they were fed at the appropriate time. Oh they were al
l breast fed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 You had a few young ones all at the same time didn't you?
