me, come in my boy, he said, here's the chef, he made me a lovely dinner. And I'm dying to shave 'cos there's another cricket match same day. I look back and my - my two fellows helping me - eeh one connected with - Charles Robers, not Charles Roberts - s
omebody at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14287354\charrsid4527623 Bellevue }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 
worked - he was a big man in Wakefield anyway he died at sea, they buried him at sea and when I got back I was unshaven. I'd got me razor and all that - do it there. So he said, where have you been? Oh I said, I made him look over there,
 I nearly told him to go to - oh, he said, I'm sorry. I said, have you seen the ground? You didn't see it last night did you? Aye, I saw it. It were an eyesore. I said, look at it now. Beautiful. Ready for cricket normal bat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 How long did you do this for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Eight and a half years. And I never took a penny off them. I didn't want their ten bob.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 You take an interest in Yorkshire don't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes. Yes. Oh I've been to the Yorkshire forty odd years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 What about football?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Yes, I do - 
I help my friend Norman Arthur. Anyway, look, I ran - or at least I organised from the Manor House at Hill which Charlie Bullock kept, I organised five tours, cricket tours. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15679127 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Whereabouts were they to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9445534 DL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 Devon. Cornwall. Buckingham. I could hav
e gone overseas if I'd wanted. I thought no. Anyway my dearest tour was ten pounds four and six for the week. I used to get preferential terms from Wallace Arnolds. You know what they call him, he's a big man on the Leeds Corporation now. No, no, not Barr
. He's Conservative. Fielder. Oh yes, he was one who would do, yes. Well - we stayed at the same}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14287354\charrsid4527623  hotel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 
 for five years, the Avenue Hotel, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14287354\charrsid4527623 Belgrave}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623  Road, Torq}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14287354\charrsid4527623 u}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 ay. Oh we'd one wet day }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14287354\charrsid4527623 in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14111555\charrsid4527623 
 five years. Yes. And I made fixtures at all the leading clubs you know. Smashing teams.
