I used to tell them the night before, I said, look - if you're not up and down breakfast I'm going without you. No, I will not be late when we're playing }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14287354\charrsid4527623 the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
